om turn-over ball on the Blitzboks' tryline after some sublime defence.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blitzboks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leyds' try\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"a counter\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"turn-over ball\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"some sublime defence\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand hit back two minutes after the buzzer with a try by Moses Leo, with Andrew Knewstubb adding the conversion to make it 14-7 at the break.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.286905631960263e-13, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses\", \"score\": 0.9999999746196412, \"rank\": 1.821455237257699e-08, \"text\": \"Moses\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses\"}, {\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9892534210933428, \"rank\": 0.010512173058078765, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_